### ============================================
### CATEGORY API TESTING
### ============================================
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. GET ALL CATEGORIES (Default pagination)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 2. GET CATEGORIES WITH PAGINATION
### Page 0, Size 10
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. SEARCH CATEGORIES BY NAME
### Search for "Electronics"
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?search=Electronics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. FILTER CATEGORIES BY STATUS
### Get only active categories
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 5. SEARCH + FILTER BY STATUS
### Search "Food" in active categories only
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?search=Food&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. SORT CATEGORIES BY NAME (Ascending)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?sortBy=name&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 7. SORT CATEGORIES BY CREATED DATE (Descending)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 8. CREATE NEW CATEGORY - Electronics (Auto-generate slug)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics"
}

